                     <interp inst="t17861025-58-off327" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17861025-58-off327" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17861025-58-cd328" type="crimeDate">9th day of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861025-58-off327 t17861025-58-cd328"></join>, a black gelding, value 26 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17861025-58-victim741" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Kirkman
                  <interp inst="t17861025-58-victim741" type="surname" value="Kirkman"></interp>
